JUSTIN KOSSLYN: Thank
you Andrei and Irina

00:00:07.310 --> 00:00:09.110
for joining us here today.

00:00:09.110 --> 00:00:11.870
At Google, we talk a
lot about the user.

00:00:11.870 --> 00:00:14.240
I spent two and a half years
in Mountain View as a PM

00:00:14.240 --> 00:00:15.330
on couple of different products.

00:00:15.330 --> 00:00:16.871
And whenever I talked
about the user,

00:00:16.871 --> 00:00:18.360
