00:00:18.360 --> 00:00:20.900
And that dashboard would have
various numbers and graphs

00:00:20.900 --> 00:00:23.512
of the number of users in
different countries, the level

00:00:23.512 --> 00:00:25.970
of engagement that they had on
a day to day or week to week

00:00:25.970 --> 00:00:26.880
basis.

00:00:26.880 --> 00:00:28.319
And that was my touch point.

00:00:28.319 --> 00:00:30.110
But I think why I'm so
grateful that you're

00:00:30.110 --> 00:00:32.840
