issue for Google.

00:00:39.430 --> 00:00:41.780
Our mission is to organize
the world's information,

00:00:41.780 --> 00:00:43.404
make it accessible and useful.

00:00:43.404 --> 00:00:44.820
And that is what
you do every day.

00:00:44.820 --> 00:00:47.750
You organize information on
very sensitive, very challenging

00:00:47.750 --> 00:00:49.820
topics, and you make it
accessible and useful

00:00:49.820 --> 00:00:51.110
to the world.

00:00:51.110 --> 00:00:52.700
And so my hope
today is that we can

00:00:52.700 --> 00:00:56.360
