00:39:45.005 --> 00:39:47.070
AUDIENCE: It's somewhat
ironic that today

00:39:47.070 --> 00:39:49.210
is Putin's 65th birthday.

00:39:49.210 --> 00:39:51.590
And as "The Economist"
