00:46:59.910 --> 00:47:05.100
think that it always started
with something nonpolitical

00:47:05.100 --> 00:47:07.166
like torrents websites
and pornography.

00:47:07.166 --> 00:47:12.615
And this has shifted
very soon to politics,

00:47:12.615 --> 00:47:17.310
because to block pornography
websites is also politics.

00:47:17.310 --> 00:47:18.780
It's a restriction.

